incide_enDescription: The cult beauty product. Clarins Beauty Flash Balm is an instant radiance-booster which zaps all signs of fatigue. Perfect for any time of day, the flash balm preps skin for make-up application like no other. Make-up glides on like a dream, refining the skin's texture with an almost unbelievable staying power. A multitasking moisturiser, mask and make-up base: apply a thin layer over the entire face after cleansing and toning (do not rub in) and follow with make-up. Alternatively, the Clarins beauty flash balm can be applied in a thicker layer 2-3 times a week as an intensive beauty treatment mask - leave it on for 10-15 minutes each time, removing all excess with water. Tone and moisturise as usual with products suitable for your skin type. Active ingredients: Witch Hazel and Olive tree extracts tighten and promote radiance Algae extract revitalises Bisabolol soothes and softens Rice Starch purifies the epidermis
